# Environment Variables Template
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Fill in your actual API keys below
# 3. NEVER commit .env.local to git (it's in .gitignore)
# 4. Restart dev server after changing these values

# ============================================
# REQUIRED - Google Maps API Key
# ============================================
# Get your key from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
#
# IMPORTANT SECURITY SETUP:
# 1. Create a new API key (don't reuse existing keys)
# 2. Restrict the key to only your domain:
#    - In Google Cloud Console, go to APIs & Services > Credentials
#    - Edit your API key > Application restrictions > HTTP referrers
#    - Add: yourdomain.com/* and localhost:5173/*
# 3. Restrict to only these APIs:
#    - Maps JavaScript API
#    - Places API (if using autocomplete)
# 4. Set usage quotas to prevent runaway costs
#
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

# ============================================
# OPTIONAL - SimplyRETS MLS API Credentials
# ============================================
# Get your credentials from: https://simplyrets.com/
# For demo/testing, use: simplyrets / simplyrets
#
# WARNING: These credentials should ONLY be used server-side
# The current implementation is commented out for security
# See SECURITY.md for proper implementation using Cloudflare Workers
#
VITE_SIMPLYRETS_API_KEY=
VITE_SIMPLYRETS_API_SECRET=

# Your MLS Agent ID (Optional - filters MLS results to only YOUR listings)
# Leave blank to show all MLS properties (useful for testing with sample data)
# Example: VITE_AGENT_MLS_ID=ABC12345
VITE_AGENT_MLS_ID=
